TY  - JOUR
AU  - Ericsson, Neil R.
T1  - Asymptotic Properties of Instrumental Variables Statistics for Testing Non-Nested Hypotheses
PY  - 1983
Y1  - 1983/04/01
DO  - 10.2307/2297417
JO  - The Review of Economic Studies
JA  - Rev Econ Stud
VL  - 50
IS  - 2
SP  - 287
EP  - 304
SN  - 0034-6527
AB  - This paper develops Instrumental Variables statistics for testing non-nested hypotheses when the hypotheses considered are single equations from a system of linear dynamic simultaneous equations. Asymptotic distributions of those statistics and of comparable Maximum Likelihood statistics are derived under the null hypothesis, a local non-nested alternative hypothesis, and a local “comprehensive” alternative hypothesis. The asymptotic powers of the non-nested hypothesis tests are compared with those of tests of nested hypotheses, and a numerical application is given.
Y2  - 3/25/2024
UR  - https://doi.org/10.2307/2297417
ER  - 



